    <!-- About Content Section -->
    <div class="container">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>At EduGaming, we believe that learning should be fun and engaging. Our platform offers a range of educational games designed to help children and teens develop their skills in a fun and interactive way. Whether you are looking to improve your math skills or learn more about science, our games are designed to make learning enjoyable and effective.</p>

        <p>Our team consists of educators, game designers, and developers who are passionate about education and technology. We work together to create games that are not only educational but also entertaining, ensuring that students are motivated and engaged in their learning journey.</p>

        <p>Join us today and discover a new way to learn with EduGaming!</p>
    </div>

